Space Game Template ( Game Ready and Render Ready) :


We all love space! Space exploration game inside Unreal Engine 5 looks stunning. This Asset is a template to make your space exploration game or any space game. It includes 15 unique alien planets(fully customizable) you can generate different alien planets by manipulating the settings . Also this includes 5 Sci-Fi spaceships (Fully controllable/Drivable) , Asteroid Blueprint- you can make an asteroid field/ asteroid planet ring with the help of this blueprint (also you can add your own asteroid mesh) , the blueprint is fully customizable. Game ready scenes, just hit the play button and explore!


Alien Planets:

  • 15 unique Alien Planets
  • High resolution textures (8k)
  • Customizable Planet materials ( you can create different alien planets with the settings)
  • Realistic and Cinematic Planets


Types:

  • Desert
  • Terrestrial
  • Rocky
  • Gas Giants
  • Thick Atmospheric


Asteroid Blueprints:

  • Customizable blueprint to create planet ring/ asteroid field
  • You can add your own asteroid mesh
  • Can create rings, asteroid field, asteroid belts


Sci-Fi Space Ships:

  • Drivable Space Ship pawns
  • Realistic and Dynamic Movement
  • 5 unique spaceships


Types:

  • Sci-Fi alien ship
  • Space cruiser
  • Sci-Fi personal ship
  • Sci-fi speeder
  • Warp Shuttle


Inputs:

  • Forward (W)
  • Acceleration/ Boost (W and Shift)
  • Slow down/ Stop (S)
  • Left-Right movement (A and D and Mouse X)
  • Rotation ( Mouse X, Mouse Y and Q and E)



Space skyboxes:

  • 4 different space skyboxes
  • High resolution (8k)
  • Customizable materials


Types:

  • Blue galaxy
  • Galaxy
  • Stars
  • Blue Stars


The scenes are Game ready and you can create beautiful space renders also. Create awesome Sci-Fi projects , cinematics and games with this template!!!

Don't forget to check the documentation for setting up the Input mappings.


Documentation


Note:( In the world setting please tick the ' Enable large world' option and in the game mode override of the world setting, please select - ship_gamemode_BP. Check the controls in the documentation. Explore the template and Enjoy!!)
